Constructor Detail

BufferedRawData

public BufferedRawData(byte functionCode,
                       byte sensorCode,
                       byte channelBitmask,
                       int[][] values)
Constructor of a BufferedRawData object. This is used by the lower level components of the framework for creating BufferedRawData objects from a low level BufferedRawData data packet received by remote nodes.

Parameters:
functionCode - the function code
sensorCode - the sensor code
channelBitmask - the sensor channels bitmask
values - the channels values matrix (rows are the samples, columns are the channels)
See Also:
SPINEFunctionConstants, SPINESensorConstants
